[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     11[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     12[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Recipe 12.10 is a strong, technically grounded treatment of real-time physiological waveform analysis in the ICU. The Problem section is compelling and accurately conveys the data loss problem in bedside monitoring. The Technology section teaches signal processing and deep learning fundamentals well, with appropriate depth on artifact handling, class imbalance, and regulatory constraints. The architecture is sound for the stated use case, and the alert fatigue discussion reflects genuine production experience.
