[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     16[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The recipe has no CRITICAL findings and 2 HIGH findings. Both are addressable with targeted additions. The architecture is production-viable, the security posture is mostly well-considered, and the healthcare domain treatment is accurate. The FDA/SaMD discussion is appropriately cautious and correctly framed.
